        {
            "title": "粉嶺走失鸚鵡樹上喚「爸爸」 消防救下人鳥重聚",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"麥先生與愛鳥重聚。許文光攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/af483b376c3866c95dc356d788ebdf66/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250221/_2025022112342862134.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">麥先生與愛鳥重聚。許文光攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>粉嶺一隻愛叫「爸爸」的鸚鵡，兩日前走失，主人麥先生四處張貼街招尋雀，今（21日）晨10時許，途人行經吉祥街一棵大樹旁，聽到「爸爸、爸爸」聲音，思疑有人獨留兒童在家，通知屋苑保安，保安查看證實是一隻鸚鵡，主人聞訊趕至，由消防員升雲梯將鸚鵡救下，最終人雀重聚。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094619/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"麥先生喜與愛鳥重聚。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/626bb7954017c418e1febeb559454b4d/2025-02/01_1_29.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        麥先生喜與愛鳥重聚。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094620/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"人鳥重逢，麥先生眉開眼笑。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e47ece9c47c57ff6c02473f7840b7e5a/2025-02/02_1_31.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        人鳥重逢，麥先生眉開眼笑。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094621/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"麥先生與街坊講述事件始末。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/02ceffd2e257c81b5820b8240b6aa297/2025-02/03_2_9.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        麥先生與街坊講述事件始末。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094622/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鸚鵡在樹上。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/55d49211d7e8950afc920f830c56382a/2025-02/04_1_14.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鸚鵡在樹上。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094623/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防到場救鳥。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/df84be8e32e54b3e1f42a8851d10b4b4/2025-02/05_1_11.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防到場救鳥。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094624/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防到場救鳥。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e588ab93d4581e7339aa47f06524b843/2025-02/06_1_9.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防到場救鳥。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094625/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防到場救鳥。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/770fb8f029ff76fd67d6f830ba7c07af/2025-02/07_1_3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防到場救鳥。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>麥指出，該鸚鵡已十歲，是朋友飼養，半年前，因移民託他照顧，他居住天台，兩日前，他將鸚鵡從雀架過手臂，殊料一輛電單車馳過，鸚鵡受轟隆引擎聲所嚇，拍翼高飛，一去不返。\n\n</p>\n<p>麥焦急尋找，四處張貼街招尋鳥，今晨10時左右，有途人行經吉祥街，聽到樹上傳來怪聲「爸爸、爸爸」，附近學校師生也聽到，擔心有人獨留兒童在家，於是通知屋苑保安，保安細看下，證實是一隻鸚鵡在樹上，聯想起尋鳥街招，遂通知麥先生過來，麥確認是走失的愛鳥，於是報警，消防到場將鸚鵡救下歸還麥先生，鸚鵡很懂性地站在主人手臂上，麥眉開眼笑。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2054082/即時-港聞-粉嶺走失鸚鵡樹上喚-爸爸-消防救下人鳥重聚",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-21 12:42:03",
