            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "紅豆首映｜朱鑑然遇前度盧慧敏Amy Lo 分手多年仍感不安 即使劇情需要也不願演情侶",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/acc39c1077be8b493e0d90a2c55e85a9/2025-02/page_272.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/60c6e307f00771efaa2c4177d1c00102/0728e0f1a7b34d4fb909841c68480060-abf806df1d2a580bf5da83c0307072d9-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67b8007717ba4\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67b8007717ba6\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"紅豆｜朱鑑然遇前度盧慧敏Amy Lo 分手多年仍感尷尬不安 即使劇情需要也不願演情侶\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/52f0cc1c59ca29fe20c20563e2efefa1/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250221/_2025022111522676966.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">紅豆｜朱鑑然遇前度盧慧敏Amy Lo 分手多年仍感尷尬不安 即使劇情需要也不願演情侶</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>朱鑑然和盧慧敏（Amy Lo）這對舊情人昨晚（20日）到銅鑼灣出席有份主演的電影《紅豆》的慈善首映禮。記者問到這次再合作是否感到尷尬？朱鑑然表示︰「有，很尷尬，也很不安，想即刻離開。」Amy即對他說「不要這樣」。\n\n</p><h2>朱鑑然支支吾吾</h2>\n<p>Amy續指︰「其實很開心一起參與拍攝一套溫馨電影，一起工作時就像家人似的，真的很溫暖。」追問朱鑑然若然要他和Amy飾演情侶，是否願意？他第一時間表示「不願意」，之後才說：「正常地劇本要我做甚麼就做甚麼，剛剛說不安只是說笑而已。」Amy則指出，十分珍惜拍港產片扮演不同角色的機會，就算與朱鑑然飾演情侶也會接受。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關文章︰<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/film-drama/3411571/%E7%B4%85%E8%B1%86%E4%B8%A8%E4%BB%BB%E9%81%94%E8%8F%AF%E8%88%87%E9%BE%94%E6%85%88%E6%81%A935%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E5%B7%B2%E6%BC%94%E5%A4%AB%E5%A6%BB%E6%9C%89%E5%85%85%E8%B6%B3%E9%BB%98%E5%A5%91-%E8%87%AA%E8%AA%8D%E8%81%BD%E8%80%81%E5%A9%86%E8%A9%B1%E4%BD%86%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93-%E6%9C%B1%E9%91%91%E7%84%B6%E7%82%BA%E6%96%B0%E6%88%B2%E5%AD%B8%E6%96%B0%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E7%B7%B4%E5%88%B0%E8%86%8A%E9%A0%AD%E7%97%9B\">紅豆丨任達華與龔慈恩35年前已演夫妻有充足默契 自認聽老婆話但仍有改善空間 朱鑑然為新戲學新運動練到膊頭痛</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094386/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"盧慧敏、朱鑑然這對舊情人出席離島扶輪社《紅豆》慈善首映禮。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3b9737000296d3a6a31af895255119e7/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_23_53_58_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        盧慧敏、朱鑑然這對舊情人出席離島扶輪社《紅豆》慈善首映禮。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094392/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"朱鑑然在2021年暗示和盧慧敏分手。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9817dfcd51652b0a4e1451e9ff6748d2/2025-02/w644_1__0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱鑑然在2021年暗示和盧慧敏分手。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094413/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"2019年朱鑑然被爆與盧慧敏拍拖。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7a6a85eeeae4bcf13259a7657907b0cc/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_23_53_57.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        2019年朱鑑然被爆與盧慧敏拍拖。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094416/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"盧慧敏、朱鑑然再見亦是朋友，在工作上合作，要演情侶都會接受。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b7563bdfcd22b899a3d47bee99a89cc7/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_23_53_58.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        盧慧敏、朱鑑然再見亦是朋友，在工作上合作，要演情侶都會接受。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094418/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"朱鑑然話與盧慧敏同場感到不安是說笑。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e680558427c4ea306dec641d6a09800b/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_23_53_59_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱鑑然話與盧慧敏同場感到不安是說笑。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094419/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"《紅豆》「父女」任達華、鄧麗欣Stephy出席首映禮。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9bf3142ed2f1fcc81c568a9c9ef291a5/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_23_53_59_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《紅豆》「父女」任達華、鄧麗欣Stephy出席首映禮。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094420/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"盧慧敏在電影圈經驗尚淺。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dd51fc53140d4da541529d61ff82cc70/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_23_53_59.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        盧慧敏在電影圈經驗尚淺。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094421/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"任達華攬攬馮素波。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/378bd1753f1d0f3b68f05635b2ca01a3/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_23_54_00_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        任達華攬攬馮素波。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094422/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"《紅豆》任達華、龔慈恩是對父妻。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/08e7855082f4a420074af7c9dc72e95d/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_23_54_00.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《紅豆》任達華、龔慈恩是對父妻。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4094429/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"朱鑑然、盧慧敏喜與馮素波合作，向前前輩學習。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1ba01e2915f65cae670ca913242ad647/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-20_at_23_54_05.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朱鑑然、盧慧敏喜與馮素波合作，向前前輩學習。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>未能合體謝票</h2>\n<p>問到二人幾時合體謝票？朱鑑然表示，剛剛開拍一套新戲，也希望盡量抽時間出席謝票活動。此外，Amy希望向唱歌方面發展，並稱眼看鄧麗欣為演唱會積極準備，勤力健身令身形狀態甚佳，會以對方作為學習目標。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
